And the time before that.

12:27.291 --> 12:28.959
- I mean,
- this is what y'all do.

12:28.962 --> 12:30.125
- I mean, one minute
- she's telling me,

12:30.128 --> 12:32.291
- "Come over.
- Let's try to get pregnant."

12:32.295 --> 12:34.625
- Next thing I know, she's talking
- about signs from God

12:34.629 --> 12:35.916
And telling me to leave.

12:35.917 --> 12:37.083
- Well, at least
- you can credit her

12:37.086 --> 12:38.373
For bringing in an expert.

12:38.375 --> 12:39.415
Yeah, whatever.

12:39.417 --> 12:40.874
This is exactly the reason

12:40.875 --> 12:41.792
- I stopped messing
- with black women.

12:41.795 --> 12:44.373
Okay, I'ma lend you an ear,

12:44.375 --> 12:45.875
- but you're not gonna talk
- out the side of your neck

12:45.879 --> 12:47.415
About black women.

12:47.417 --> 12:49.083
- I'm married
- to a black woman.

12:49.086 --> 12:50.540
My mother's a black woman.

12:50.542 --> 12:51.731
And we're not gonna let

12:51.732 --> 12:52.916
Mary Jane define this moment

12:52.917 --> 12:54.415
for all black women.

12:54.417 --> 12:55.749
Sorry, man. Sorry.

12:55.750 --> 12:57.291
- Besides, what's going on
- with you and Mary Jane

12:57.295 --> 12:59.125
- Has nothing to do
- with her being black.

12:59.128 --> 13:00.168
It's about you

13:00.169 --> 13:01.207
both being too prideful

13:01.208 --> 13:02.751
and too hardheaded about getting

13:02.752 --> 13:04.290
your life together, all right?

13:04.291 --> 13:05.334
Both of you to blame

13:05.335 --> 13:06.373
for games you played

13:06.375 --> 13:07.793
and the times you've wasted,

13:07.794 --> 13:09.207
and just like I told you,

13:09.208 --> 13:10.730
Ana was gonna try to cash in

13:10.731 --> 13:12.248
on that modeling career.

13:12.250 --> 13:13.957
Ah.

13:13.959 --> 13:16.207
Truth got a man drinking.

13:16.208 --> 13:17.582
Well, don't drink too much

13:17.583 --> 13:19.083
- and forget about what we
- talked about, all right?

13:19.086 --> 13:20.251
'Cause I am tired

13:20.252 --> 13:21.415
of this conversation, D.

13:21.417 --> 13:23.459
You got me and Valerie

13:23.460 --> 13:25.498
arguing about you two,

13:25.500 --> 13:26.790
and we don't have any problems

13:26.792 --> 13:27.876
except trying

13:27.877 --> 13:28.957
to figure out y'all's.

13:28.959 --> 13:30.917
I don't want that.

13:32.500 --> 13:33.916
All right, look.

13:33.917 --> 13:35.375
- I was no saint in this.
- I know that.

13:35.378 --> 13:37.291
- I wasn't the best
- communicator. Great.

13:37.295 --> 13:38.688
But I never lied to that girl,

13:38.689 --> 13:40.081
not one time, not once.

13:40.083 --> 13:41.166
- Dude,
- just because you didn't lie

13:41.170 --> 13:44.332
Doesn't mean you communicated.

13:44.333 --> 13:46.373
That's what I said.

13:46.375 --> 13:49.083
Oh. Then own it.

