14:28.083 --> 14:29.250
- (Niecy)
- Please, Auntie.

14:29.253 --> 14:30.291
- (Mary Jane)
- I'm coming over.

14:30.295 --> 14:31.834
- (Niecy)
- No.

14:31.837 --> 14:33.125
- (Mary Jane) - I have something
- I need to say to you.

14:33.128 --> 14:34.709
- (Niecy) - No, Auntie, not today.
- I am busy.

14:34.712 --> 14:36.291
- (Mary Jane)
- I'm coming over.

14:36.295 --> 14:38.207
[knocking at door]

14:38.208 --> 14:40.081
Come in.

14:40.083 --> 14:42.001
(Mary Jane)

14:42.002 --> 14:43.916
Hey.

14:43.917 --> 14:46.123
You know, Auntie,

14:46.125 --> 14:48.290
I really am having a good day,

14:48.291 --> 14:49.814
probably the best day

14:49.815 --> 14:51.332
I had in a while.

14:51.333 --> 14:52.876
I really don't want to do this.

14:52.877 --> 14:54.415
I really don't.

14:54.417 --> 14:56.081
Do what?

14:56.083 --> 14:57.730
Girl, I come in peace

14:57.731 --> 14:59.373
and reconciliation.

14:59.375 --> 15:00.707
Seriously.

15:00.709 --> 15:02.458
- You know,
- it's times like this

15:02.462 --> 15:04.584
Where I see merit

15:04.585 --> 15:06.709
in paying my own rent.

15:08.542 --> 15:10.248
And I ain't saying nothing,

15:10.250 --> 15:12.064
because I know that doesn't work

15:12.065 --> 15:13.874
between you and I.

15:13.875 --> 15:15.376
So whatever you have to say,

15:15.377 --> 15:16.874
say it.

15:16.875 --> 15:18.334
- Or better yet,
- you can email it.

15:18.337 --> 15:19.605
I'm good

15:19.606 --> 15:20.874
about checking my email.

15:20.875 --> 15:22.606
Can you alert me

15:22.607 --> 15:24.332
