15:24.333 --> 15:26.125
- And that's a great use
- of your vocabulary words,

15:26.128 --> 15:27.165
By the way.

15:27.166 --> 15:28.834
Whatever.

15:34.500 --> 15:36.375
Mm.

15:40.542 --> 15:42.081
[chuckles]

15:42.083 --> 15:43.875
- I think I look good.
- I think I look good.

15:43.879 --> 15:45.707
I love you too much, Niecy,

15:45.709 --> 15:47.165
