21:16.712 --> 21:18.624
With a laugh and a chuckle.

21:18.625 --> 21:20.855
But, uh, meanwhile,

21:20.856 --> 21:23.081
back at the ranch,

21:23.083 --> 21:24.855
I'm calling to talk business,

21:24.856 --> 21:26.624
so, um,

21:26.625 --> 21:28.084
I'm taking your advice

21:28.085 --> 21:29.540
